	<div class="bodysection bodysection-white">
	<div class="container notop nobot">
		<div class="mainsection postcols clearfix">
						<div class="maincol">
			<div class="maincol-a notop nobot">	
				<div class="postcontent">
					
<p>Crispy, sticky, sweet, and savory &mdash; these <strong>Air Fryer Honey Glazed Pork Belly Bites</strong> are exactly the kind of recipe that turns a regular weeknight into something special. Make a batch, share with friends, and don&rsquo;t be surprised when they ask you for the recipe.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img data-perfmatters-preload fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="760" height="760" data-pin-description="Crispy, sticky, sweet, and savory &mdash; these Air Fryer Honey Glazed Pork Belly Bites are exactly the kind of recipe that turns a regular weeknight into something special. Make a batch, share with friends, and don&#039;t be surprised when they ask you for the recipe." data-pin-title="Air Fryer Honey Glazed Pork Belly Bites " src="https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites-760x760.png" alt="Air fryer honey glazed pork belly bites garnished with sesame seeds and green onions on a white plate" class="wp-image-194449" srcset="https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites-760x760.png 760w, https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites-380x380.png 380w, https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites-150x150.png 150w, https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites-768x768.png 768w, https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites-500x500.png 500w, https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites-600x600.png 600w, https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites-96x96.png 96w, https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites-160x160.png 160w, https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites-320x320.png 320w, https://forktospoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Air-Fryer-Honey-Glazed-Pork-Belly-Bites.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) calc(100vw - 40px), 760px"></figure><div class="fluentform ff-default fluentform_wrapper_3 ffs_custom_wrap"><form data-form_id="3" id="fluentform_3" class="frm